      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To provide that rates of pay for Members of Congress shall not be subject to automatic adjustment; and to provide that any bill or resolution, and any amendment to any bill or resolution, which would increase Members' pay may be adopted only by a recorded vote.</title>
